headline: 3 S&P 500 Stocks Facing Headwinds
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.

headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid AVY and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Avery Dennison’s shares (currently trading at $179.87) have posted a disappointing 11.8% loss while the S&P 500 was flat. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
